Name: ENT00000058
Entity_Name__c:
SELECT Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Name,
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.HPLMN_Operator_Tadig__c,
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Open_Date_Formula__c,
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.SO_Type__c,
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.VPLMN_Operator_Tadig__c,
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Financial_Direction__c,
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Footprint__r.HPLMN_HUB_TADIG_Code__c,
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Footprint__r.VPLMN_HUB_TADIG_Code__c
FROM
    Footprint_Service_Detail__c
WHERE
((((Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Footprint__r.HPLMN__r.Force_Financial_Report__c = True AND Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Status__c in ( 'Pending','Progressing','Selected','Open','Migrate' )) OR (Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Footprint__r.HPLMN__r.Force_Financial_Report__c = False AND Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Status__c in('Open','Migrate','Progressing') AND Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Product__c in ('GSM','GPRS') )) AND Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Financial_Direction__c in ('Bilateral','Unilateral Outbound') AND Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Open_Date_Formula__c  != NULL ) AND ((Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.HPLMN_Operator_Tadig__c not in ('IND20','IND21','IND22','IND23','IND24','INDT1','INDT3','INDT4','INDT5','INDT6','INDT7','INDT8','INDT9','INDTB','INDTG','INDTH','INDTK','INDTO','INDTP','INDTR') or Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.VPLMN_Operator_Tadig__c != 'NLDLT' ) and ( Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.VPLMN_Operator_Tadig__c not in ('IND20','IND21','IND22','IND23','IND24','INDT1','INDT3','INDT4','INDT5','INDT6','INDT7','INDT8','INDT9','INDTB','INDTG','INDTH','INDTK','INDTO','INDTP','INDTR') or Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.HPLMN_Operator_Tadig__c != 'NLDLT' ))) AND Footprint_Service_Detail__c.Footprint_Service__r.Has_Test_Account__c = False

Name: ENT00000099
Entity_Name__c:
SELECT
    Active_Contract_Agreement_to_Deliver__c,
    Effective_Contract_Type__c,
    HSF_Trigger__c,
    Name,
    Pay_Currency__c,
    Receive_Currency__c,
    TADIG_Code__c,
    VRS_Start_Date__c,
    DCH__r.TADIG_Code__c,
    FCH_Invoice_Creation__r.TADIG_Code__c,
    FCH_Reconciliation__r.TADIG_Code__c,
    FCH_Settlement__r.TADIG_Code__c
FROM Account WHERE
Record_Type__c = 'Operator' AND ((Status__c = 'Onboarded' OR Status__c = 'Contract Completed') OR Contract_Status__c = 'Contract Completed') AND VRS_Start_Date__c != NULL AND Test_Account__c = false
